      <div id="settingGoalsSection" >         
        <h2 class="text-center">Setting Goals</h2>
        <br>
        <p style="font-size:18px" class="text-justify">When setting fitness goals, it's important to set specific, measurable, achievable, relevant, and time-bound (SMART) goals. For example, a SMART goal might be to run a 5K race in 30 minutes within six months. Breaking your goals down into smaller, more manageable steps can also help you stay motivated and on track.</p>
        <br>
      </div>

      <div id="creatingAPlanSection" >         
        <h2 class="text-center">Creating a Plan</h2>
        <br>

      <div class="container">
      <div class="row">  
      <div class="col-sm">
      <br>
      <br>
        <p style="font-size:18px" class="text-justify">Once you have set your fitness goals, create a plan to achieve them. This could include scheduling your workouts, finding a workout buddy or joining a fitness class, tracking your progress, and adjusting your plan as needed.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm text-center">
        <img src="https://www.xero.com/content/dam/xero/pilot-images/guides/planning---performance/Plan-Performance-Plans-Hero.1646877603214.png" alt="Runner" width="355" height="200" class="rounded mx-auto d-block">
      </div>
      </div>
      </div> 

      <br>
      </div>  

      <div id="benefitsOfExerciseSection" >    
        <h2 class="text-center">Benefits of exercise</h2>
        <br>
       
      <div class="container">
      <div class="row">  
      <div class="col-sm text-center">
        <img src="https://prod-ne-cdn-media.puregym.com/media/805727/sc0011_improve-your-mental-health-2x.jpg?quality=80" alt="Runner" width="355" height="200" class="rounded mx-auto d-block">
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm">
        <p style="font-size:18px" class="text-justify">Regular exercise can have many benefits, such as:</p>
         <ul style="font-size:18px">
          <li>Improved cardiovascular health</li>
          <li>Increased muscle strength and endurance</li>
          <li>Better sleep</li>
          <li>Reduced stress and anxiety</li>
          <li>Improved mood and mental health</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      </div>
      </div> 
       
        <br>
      </div>
      
      <div id="typesOfExerciseSection" > 
